019package org.apache.commons.compress.archivers;
020
021/**
022 * Provides information about ArchiveEntry stream offsets.
023 */
024public interface EntryStreamOffsets {
025
026    /**
027     * Indicates that the offset is unknown.
028     */
029    long OFFSET_UNKNOWN = -1;
030
031    /**
032     * Gets the offset of data stream within the archive file,
033     *
034     * @return the offset of entry data stream, {@code OFFSET_UNKNOWN} if not known.
035     */
036    long getDataOffset();
037
038    /**
039     * Tests whether the stream is contiguous, that is, not split among several archive parts, interspersed with control blocks, and so on.
040     *
041     * @return true if stream is contiguous, false otherwise.
042     */
043    boolean isStreamContiguous();
044}
